  <brief_summary>
    <textblock>
      The purpose of this study is to determine how feedback and practice affect decision making in
      adolescents with attention deficit and hyperactivity disorder.

      Participants will have to choose between low and certain outcome and a higher but uncertain
      outcome, with or without serial feedback after each trial. Participants will perform the task
      twice to examine practice effects.
    </textblock>
  </brief_summary>
